<title>Mini Spreadsheet</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
  h1 { margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.5em; }

  #app-container { 
    width: 600px; 
    height: 400px; 
